ЁЯУЭ Summary (English)

You are given 3 integers A, B, and C.
You need to check whether the average of A and B ( (A + B) / 2 ) is strictly greater than C.

If (A + B) / 2 > C, print YES.

Otherwise, print NO.

This must be done for T test cases.

